project_descr: The project aims at supporting the National TB and HIV Programs to accelerate the implementation of National Strategic Plan in order to reduce the HIV and TB burden in Djibouti

outputs.output_descr: The main objective of this project is to improve access to care and quality of care for TB patients including the most vulnerable including children, refugees, and prisoners
